{"tid":1752701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"鎅票撚，白票撚，知唔知你地斷送左關鍵一席","createTime":"2019-11-24T23:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T04:08:27.000Z","uid":233317,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ed60ca6f4bf3848091735f46fa106b3ca3c35b74","tid":1752701,"uid":233317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T23:02:44.000Z","msg":"如果民選區議員議席唔夠45個嘅話，保皇黨係連提名三個超區都做唔到，係選都冇得選，直接dq呀！！！！<br />\n而家仲搞到下年分分鐘要辛辛苦苦，又配票又剩咁，先可以保住三席。<br />\n如果保皇黨提名得兩個，下年分分鐘黃營博四席都仲得。就算唔想博第四席，至少可以出十個人出黎鳩撼，唔洗因為配票含淚投泛民。<br />\n區選含淚，點都好過立會含淚吖。"},{"pid":"0c478d684b5792ff1a0b67adb4ce8edc721f4073","tid":1752701,"uid":233317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T23:04:07.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"6c79524a377ac0834c729f6d942409f4323407df","tid":1752701,"uid":233317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T23:04:17.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"8865d353887eb2c0d4e8d95c6a7ae650a71e0eb4","tid":1752701,"uid":233317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T23:06:40.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"f6b75dd8088af108f62af2d426dbfd142d369315","tid":1752701,"uid":233317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T23:07:55.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"a74183bea37774825a3beb5f28e2aba0fa11e642","tid":1752701,"uid":233317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T23:09:34.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"567d807a4997f70896d7860a3d4c7a5b61a962aa","tid":1752701,"uid":233317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T23:11:31.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"af3259edeb143ae4ba75d099bb383c919934ed19","tid":1752701,"uid":233317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T23:13:49.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"49889ecf9a6320dadad95d77d68f323c9d0885e8","tid":1752701,"uid":233317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T23:15:45.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"8ede41573695a0490473d9e616fbc64e42f4b61d","tid":1752701,"uid":233317,"like